Father Joseph Witko: I saw Jesus in a white robe
He is a charismatic man.
The mass for the release and healing is attended by the crowds.
He was only a few years old when things began to happen in his life.
Today, through the Franciscan, others are experiencing it.
Crowds attend Fr Witko’s Mass for Liberation and Healing
Once, the parents of a 7-month-old child who had a hole of 7.5 mm in the heart came to him.
It was to be operated on.
Father Joseph Witko prayed over him.
The same day, the boy was taken to the hospital for treatment.
The doctors were astonished and said: “The surgery is not necessary, the loss is only 1.5 mm”.
Her parents were crying for her.
After another prayer, the Franciscan hole disappeared completely.
The spiritual extraordinary actions of the Creator began to experience as a teenager.
In his dreams, purifying souls came to him asking for help.
I was awakened at night and urged to pray for the dead and those who died at the moment – he recalls.
He also experienced the presence of an evil spirit.
And he had a vision of what happens to a man who commits mortal sin.
“My body started to change.
I lost my human characteristics and began to look like an animal,” he says.
The invisible force lifted him upwards, he could not make a voice out of himself.
He felt that he was lost.
Then God showed him the salvation.
“Drenched in the waters of the river symbolising the Holy Baptism, I was released and returned to my human form...”, he says.
He did not tell anyone about these strange experiences.
His vocation matured in him.
He was 16 when he joined the Franciscans.
He did not only want to talk about Jesus in his sermons.
He wanted people to experience Him alive.
Members of the charismatic community of Renewal in the Holy Spirit
Many people who are counting on getting rid of their illness attend healing masses celebrated by Father Witko.
The priest emphasizes, however, that their main goal is spiritual healing, not physical.
